** README **
************

** Hints for running glsl-intro-shaders project in:

** Mac Mini
** MAC OS X 1.5 Leopard version

** Create symbolic link on /usr/include to OpenGL path

$ cd /usr/include
$ sudo ln -s /System/Library/Frameworks/OpenGL.framework/Headers GL

** Install GLUT

$ sudo port install glut

http://developer.apple.com/mac/library/samplecode/glut/index.html

** Download the zip, uncompress and follow ReadMe.txt

** Install glew

$ sudo port install glew

** Change Makefile to add MAC_FLAG and MAC_LINK

